sidebar_pin.description:
sidebar_pin mailbox [ mailbox ...]
sidebar_unpin { * | mailbox ... }
The **sidebar_pin** command specifies *mailbox*es that will always be displayed in the sidebar, even if \$sidebar_new_mail_only is set and the *mailbox* does not contain new mail.The **sidebar_unpin** command is used to remove a *mailbox* from the list of always displayed *mailbox*es. Use "**sidebar_unpin \***" to remove all *mailbox*es.

